text: Hilda Walterová, also Hilde Doleschell, (21 February 1915 - 19 April 2013)Obituary was a Czech alpine skier. She competed in the women's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Czech female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Liberec Category:Austrian female tennis players
